title: #300 LEGAL ACTION: Crowder Fights Twitter and YouTube!
description: Talking all things concerning Crowder’s Twitter ban, Fallout Boy’s latest Liberal initiative, French work fines, missing dogs and more. Paul Joseph Watson stops by to talk social media censorship and our half-Asian lawyer, Bill, swings by to discuss our latest action against Twitter.
